---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About First7">

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">About First7</h1>

    <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">
      First7 is built to help you develop a daily habit of faith through Scripture, reflection, and guided plans.
    </p>

    <p>
      In a world full of distractions, it’s easy to lose consistency in your spiritual life. First7 is designed to simplify that — giving you a clear, focused path to spend time with God every day.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">What You’ll Find Here</h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-muted)]">
      <li>Simple, structured Bible reading</li>
      <li>Short devotionals for daily reflection</li>
      <li>Guided plans to build consistency</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Our Goal</h2>

    <p>
      Not to overwhelm you — but to help you start small, stay consistent, and grow deeper in your faith over time.
    </p>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>